{"lastModified":1774621651666,"uri":"c::18231584005::vessel::6b031620-edd7-11ee-921f-e14926b52275","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nStep aboard the Tanna 47, a luxurious yacht with a dedicated permanent crew, offering an unparalleled sailing experience. The yacht features a thoughtfully designed U-shaped galley, complemented by a spacious opening bay door, creating a sense of expansive living with abundant natural light that highlights its elegant interior.\n\nIndulge in the innovative galley/saloon area, providing ample storage space. The redesigned layout ensures a user-friendly saloon with a lounger and an ergonomic watchkeeping station, ensuring a seamless experience under the expert guidance of our experienced crew.\n\nEnjoy the convenience of a chart table easily accessible from the helm, fostering a safe and convivial atmosphere for cruising.\n\nLuxury reaches new heights with the Tanna 47's expanded Lounge area on the flybridge. The \"Lounge deck\" layout exudes sophistication, enhancing the yacht's overall comfort during sailing. Sail serenely with easy access to maneuvers, all while enjoying seamless communication with our attentive and professional crew.","blueprint":{"name":"HELIDONI","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::6b031620-edd7-11ee-921f-e14926b52275::assets::6f238170-bc78-11ef-af9f-15f21914a970/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::6b031620-edd7-11ee-921f-e14926b52275::assets::6f215e90-bc78-11ef-af9e-15f21914a970/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::6b031620-edd7-11ee-921f-e14926b52275::assets::6f20e960-bc78-11ef-af9e-15f21914a970/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::6b031620-edd7-11ee-921f-e14926b52275::assets::6f1d8e00-bc78-11ef-af9d-15f21914a970/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::6b031620-edd7-11ee-921f-e14926b52275::assets::6f1ccab0-bc78-11ef-af9d-15f21914a970/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::6b031620-edd7-11ee-921f-e14926b52275: